  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this prospective randomized trial is to ascertain whether the use of a
      cognitive aid improves adherence to best published practices for the management of simulated
      patients regarding perioperative cardiac evaluation and management.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
